item.description:
Join us for a trip to Salem for dinner at Victoria Station, the opening of the new store "OMEN"
on Essex street, with a free concert with pagan songwriter and singer Kellianna.

We will be meeting for dinner on the Wharf at 5:00 pm at Victoria Station,
check out their website for menu below:

http://www.victoriast...

New Store "OMEN"
Check out their new website:

http://www.omensalem....

And best of all, a FREE concert from 7:00- 9:00 pm with Kellianna, you can find her website here:

http://www.kellianna....

**PLEASE NOTE**

Please state on your rsvp if you are planning on coming to dinner, and please put in your rsvp
by Thursday, April 1st so I can call in dinner reservations- THANKS! :)
item.name: Salem Trip "Omen" Opening/ Kellianna Concert
